{"tid":1773424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(反送中政制)有個方法可以以後唔駛怕黑警","createTime":"2019-12-07T12:37:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T10:54:59.000Z","uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b4544cd1ce2820bc3648c4909af133be0cc977be","tid":1773424,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T12:37:55.000Z","msg":"就係由區議會直接監督警察，制定地方治安政策，政府只提供行政支援，如派公務員支援，中央訓練警察等，具體如下:<br />\n<br />\n1.各區議會設治安委員會，負責監督警察行動，制定地方治安政策核轉立法會審核<br />\n2.區議設5治安官，代表區議會監督5警察總區之財務、人事、設施、採購、行動、犯罪率等，向區議會報告必要時司法覆核警方行動，透過政令分離，操控警政制衡警察指揮系統，如不受控將得不到資源<br />\n3.康文署/民政署/食環署/民安處設5區域康樂局/民政局/市政局/民安區，直接由各區議會指揮，政府只作後勤支援"},{"pid":"a3b3eb2781f389284603b223eb7307ec53593707","tid":1773424,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T12:38:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=dMuVdPjJf30Qxtl2jkPsRKhYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=19b2c675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tax87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftax87&d=dMuVdPjJf30Qxtl2jkPsRKhYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=2c0deeba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tax87</a>"},{"pid":"73fe7c201ede47d550e1cd0114f43a1676ee28ec","tid":1773424,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4544cd1ce2820bc3648c4909af133be0cc977be","tid":1773424,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T12:37:55.000Z","msg":"就係由區議會直接監督警察，制定地方治安政策，政府只提供行政支援，如派公務員支援，中央訓練警察等，具體如下:<br />\n<br />\n1.各區議會設治安委員會，負責監督警察行動，制定地方治安政策核轉立法會審核<br /